1
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:56,880
Yuyao.

2
00:01:58,600 --> 00:01:59,530
Come on, Sinian.

3
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,120
Let's go and see

4
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:03,180
how the little fish we released a few days ago are doing.

5
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,320
Yuyao.

6
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:18,880
Your hand.

7
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,160
What's wrong?

8
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:29,640
Yuyao.

9
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:43,800
Yuyao.

10
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,480
Yuyao.

11
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,960
Why this dream again?

12
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,080
It feels so real.

13
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:03,160
Could it be

14
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:07,370
that memorizing history has driven me crazy lately?

15
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:08,520
Yuyao.

16
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,320
Lu Sinian.

17
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:13,320
Are you going to your cram school today?

18
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,560
Yes.

19
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,800
I'm up.

20
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,400
Lu Sinian.

21
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,200
Twenty-four years old.

22
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,540
Born in August of the lunar calendar.

23
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:31,480
Single.

24
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:35,500
Preparing for the postgraduate entrance exam.

25
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:38,240
Sir,

26
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:39,800
may I ask,

27
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:41,100
who are you?

28
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:43,800
Who I am is not important.

29
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:45,760
What's important

30
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:48,079
is that you need to know

31
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:50,200
who you are.

32
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,440
I am Lu Sinian. Who am I?

33
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,880
How could I not know who I am?

34
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:57,360
Have you been troubled by dreams lately,

35
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:00,560
and keep repeating the same dream?

36
00:04:01,160 --> 00:04:02,360
As soon as you wake up,

37
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:05,460
you have heart palpitations and headaches.

38
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:07,200
Sir,

39
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,780
you don't just sell books,

40
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,130
you also tell fortunes?

41
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,900
Fortune-telling,

42
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:17,170
that's a job for the immortals.

43
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:18,760
At most,

44
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:20,810
I can interpret your dream.

45
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:38,800
Everything you see in your dreams

46
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,560
really happened.

47
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,360
That is your past life.

48
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,720
Bogda Peak

49
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,760
reflects the snow's glow,

50
00:04:50,159 --> 00:04:53,360
Jade Lake ripples with a faint green.

51
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:58,000
The lotus blooms with a thousand years of love,

52
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,840
love continues,

53
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:02,520
never to be broken.

54
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:05,360
Come.

55
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,480
Buy these books,

56
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:13,420
I guarantee you'll pass the postgraduate exam.

57
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:15,080
I'll also throw in

58
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,560
a dream interpretation for free.

59
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,360
Mister,

60
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:25,880
do I look

61
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:27,920
like a fool to you?

62
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:34,600
What happened in your past and present lives

63
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:36,280
will leave a mark.

64
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,920
It cannot be erased.

65
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:40,760
The place you saw in your dream

66
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:43,200
is Tianshan Tianchi.

67
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,720
That girl

68
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,680
is right there.

69
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:49,840
If you don't break this dream,

70
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:51,880
it won't be long before

71
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:55,120
you are lost in the dream forever.

72
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:58,520
You will never be able to break free.

73
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,040
Tianshan Tianchi.

74
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:45,960
He should like how I look in this lifetime.

75
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,400
He is finally coming.

76
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,380
Hurry up and recognize me.

77
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,360
The final test given by the Queen Mother of the West

78
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,240
is coming soon.

79
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,440
It must be a success,

80
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:16,240
not a failure.

81
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,160
You can do it.

82
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,680
Boss.

83
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,040
Is the boss here?

84
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:21,920
How do you rent these historical costumes?

85
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,130
Darling.

86
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:29,880
Do I look good in this?

87
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,640
As long as you like it,

88
00:07:31,640 --> 00:07:32,370
it suits you.

89
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:34,440
Anything that suits you looks good.

90
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:35,920
Miss.

91
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,620
How about this set?

92
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,360
You are very fair,

93
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,480
it will complement your skin tone.

94
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,640
And you are tall,

95
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:44,100
it suits you very well.

96
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,530
Darling,

97
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,130
how is it?

98
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:49,800
This one is nice.

99
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:50,659
And for you two,

100
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,720
renting costumes

101
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,780
comes with a free wishing plaque.

102
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,000
Ladies

103
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,060
and gentlemen.

104
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:02,170
We are currently flying over Tianshan's Bogda Peak,

105
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:04,640
at an altitude of 5,445 meters.

106
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:07,280
The peak is covered with snow all year round,

107
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:09,640
and Tianchi Lake at the foot of the mountain is like a mirror.

108
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:11,370
Please open your window shades

109
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:14,600
to enjoy the unique magnificence and beauty of Tianshan.

110
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:44,140
I can't believe I actually came here.

111
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:46,320
I'll stay here for a while

112
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:49,040
and see what exactly is going on.

113
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:24,500
My father must be very anxious right now.

114
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:26,920
However,

115
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,280
there is still some time before the grad school entrance exam.

116
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:31,120
He is a forgiving man

117
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,410
with a big heart.

118
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,840
He probably won't be mad, right?

119
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:38,040
That little brat.

120
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:40,160
He's really itching for a beating.

121
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:40,520
Look.

122
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,560
How dare he run away from home

123
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:43,820
without saying a word.

124
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,820
Didn't he fail the exam last year?

125
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:47,800
And this year,

126
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:49,660
he's repeating the same tragedy.

127
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,200
Look,

128
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:52,960
look at your son.

129
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,960
What has he been doing?

130
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:59,050
Wait till I get back,

131
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,490
I'll skin him alive.

132
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:04,160
Don't push Sinian too hard.

133
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:06,040
He needs a balance of work and rest.

134
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:06,440
You...

135
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:09,020
I've recently heard him in his sleep,

136
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,440
calling a girl's name.

137
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:12,100
Could he be in love?

138
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,460
This person...

139
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:51,320
Why do they look so familiar?

140
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:53,380
I feel like I've seen them somewhere.

141
00:10:57,880 --> 00:11:01,040
It seems his memories from his past life haven't been restored yet.

142
00:11:01,040 --> 00:11:03,170
I should have thought of this earlier.

143
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:10,280
This is the most successful bowl I've brewed.

144
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:11,360
After drinking this,

145
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:13,320
all your memories will be restored.

146
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,980
Let's see if I can win you over.

147
00:11:20,160 --> 00:11:21,020
Hey, handsome.

148
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:24,920
Is it your first time here?

149
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:27,480
Do you want to check out some ancient costumes in our store?

150
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,540
Ancient costumes?

151
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,210
Have some tea first.

152
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,520
It will cool you down.

153
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:33,560
Thank you.
